title: Calvin Klein Men's Slim High Stretch Jeans
description: High stretch extra soft denim for a super flexible feel and maximum comfort
Slim fit: sits below waist, slim leg
Care for your denim sustainably - wash sparingly, inside out in cold water, hang dry
Metal logo hardware and an iconic back waist logo patch
Signature omega topstitching at the back pockets

An iconic essential with super flexible high stretch denim, these reimagined jeans feature enhanced movement for maximum, all-day comfort. Updated with signature metal logo hardware and back pocket omega topstitching, a Calvin Klein hallmark. Cut in a slim fit with considered detailing and reinforced seams.
